title: Episode 311: New Body, Doesn't Count (Feat. Lexy Panterra)
itunes:title: Episode 311: New Body, Doesn't Count (Feat. Lexy Panterra)
description:
Singer/Entrepreneur, Lexy Panterra joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her latest singles "Best Friend" featuring Justin Love & "New Body," as well as her upcoming single "Booty on Her" featuring the Trina! Lexy tells a hilarious story in which one of her exes got jealous at a video shoot and started crying, she explains why she doesn't love having oral performed on her, the struggle of having her relationship hidden to the public, and much more. Enjoy!
